review_text: Amy Fritz is an organization expert per excellence. The course is awesomely practical.

All tips I learned helped me improve my productivity. I enjoyed this course because each session was short and to the point. Complete it in no time and get back to being productive. I recommend this course to you if you want to be more effective.
Actionable advice. Great if you’re not a very organized person to begin with or if you have various to-do lists and calendars and are looking to streamline your organization.
